Well here is my version of crackhouse, Hope you like it

**NOTE:** This is a deathmatch version of the map. There are no bombsites, or hostages. Alternate versions of this may be coming soon.

Creator Comment
====================
> I would say... "This is simply a remake of cs_crackhouse..." but this project took A LOT longer than I had anticipated. I wanted it to be as far from crackhouse as possible, when it came to physical appearance. While at the same time, I was very cautious about maintaining the original, key aspects of the map. I really do hope you all enjoy this map. It was a lot of hard work, but I'm glad it's finally finished!
============

**UPDATE (Nov, 24th 2014)**
- Fixed custom content implimentation.
- Removed broken Cube Mapping.
- Used default Cube Mapping.

**UPDATE (Nov, 22nd 2014)**
- Changed mapname from _cs_ to _dm_ to avoid any further confusion.
- Expanded buy zones to avoid not spawning in a buy zone.
- Attempted HDR Cube Mapping.
- Ambient Lighting raised by **10** points.

**POSSIBLE FUTURE PLANS**
- Bombsite Version
- Hostage Rescue Version

[CS:GO Version](http://gamebanana.com/csgo/maps/170723 "CS:GO Version")
Backstory:
Terrorists have been producing illegal substances in an abandoned warehouse, isolated deep in the countryside. Satellite images have shown a rise in activity in and around the warehouse, and a police unit were set to investigate. They reported that the personnel in the warehouse were heavily armed, producing illegal substances and transporting them to other locations using the old railroad.

As a Terrorist, your objective is to:
=====================================
Eliminate the attacking CTs and defend the contraband so it can be transported.

As a Counter-Terrorist, your objective is to:
============================================
Infiltrate the warehouse and eliminate the Terrorists defending the contraband so that it can be seized.

Thank you for downloading!

Features:
- .nav file for bots
- 3d skybox
- Plenty of open space for movement, also enclosed areas for ambushes
- HDR available

Updates:
- Added HDR
- Optimized to fix the FPS drop when looking across the map
- Brightened the sun
- Added more lights
- Fixed the sewers
